channel.title: Inverse - Ascent (full mix)
channel.description:
https://soundcloud.com/inverse_auxy/ascent-full-mix
I havent posted anything in like 2 months so I thought I would finally make something. Unfortunately, as I was listening to it on soundcloud it turns out the audio compression sc uses completely butchered this track to the point where it actually sounds kinda bad. However, since I have a youtube channel I uploaded it there to have full quality on the audio, so if you want it sounding decent at least go to this link instead: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uidY08vREpE
Thanks! (are youtube links allowed here or only soundcloud?)

item.dc:creator: Inverse
item.description:
I use a site called musicvid.org, their stuff is free however they only have a very limited selection of visualizers to choose from. I just modify some settings on there and add some extra stuff and its done. From there it takes a while to render and export, around 30 minutes to about an hour.
